// 2. User commits file A → checkpoint #1 (provisional)
// 3. User commits file B → checkpoint #2 (provisional)
// 4. User commits file C → checkpoint #3 (provisional)
// 5. Agent finishes (SimulateStop) → all 3 checkpoints finalized
